1. Parse/validate `providerOptions` using zod schemas
2. Build request body (prompt, size, seed, etc.)
3. Handle file input (convert to data URIs or base64)
4. Make API call using `postJsonToApi` with response handlers
5. Download generated images from URLs
6. Return images as Uint8Array with metadata

